<m0>Plantation's youth tackle football joins<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 2.57 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>new league, with room for more players<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS 1.30 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .847 INCHES<m2><ql>
<ql>
<m1><styl>ruleron<ql>
<styl>txt,1<styl>names<ql>
